title: Episode #38: Stress and Women's Health
description:
In this episode I interview Dr. Lillian Robertson on stress, the impact of toxic stress on women's health, and how to deal with stress and identity issues as women. 
Dr. Lillian is a board-certified OB/GYN and memebr of my Integrated Mind Network: https://drleaf.com/about/integrated-mind-network/lillian-robertson/
Dr. Lillian will also be a guest speaker at my 2018 conference: https://drleafconference.com
